name: Keyhole III
description:
You peer through a doorway.

You witness yourself gazing back into you.

Process: Process: A Panasonic WJ-MX50A, Panasonic WJ-MX30, Sony XV-C900 and Sony XV-C700 dreaming of each other, through each other. Direct capture played back through a Sony KV-13FM12 and rescanned via Nikon D7100 donning an Asahi SMC Takumar 1.8/55.
